Kapil Sharma is back with a bang kick starting the most awaited show 'The Kapil Sharma Show' on Sony Entertainment Television with the Badshah of Bollywood Shah Rukh Khan in Delhi. Kapil Sharma and his partners in crime, Sunil Grover, Kiku Sharda, Ali Asgar, Chandan Prabhakar and Sumona Chakravarti have laughter riot with the King of Romance Shah Rukh Khan. Sunil Grover's Gerua to Jabra Fan act with SRK in front of a packed Delhi audience is to die for. For more updates on The Kapil Sharma Show, stay tuned
